This is my first guide.

First open up client.java and search for
[code]            } else if (useItemID == 995 && atObjectID == 884)// well[/code]
then you will see
[code]            } else if (useItemID == 995 && atObjectID == 884)// well
              if(actionTimer == 0)
              if(playerHasItemAmount(995, 70000000)==false) {
	      sendMessage("You Need 70m to drop in the well");
	      }
	      else if(playerHasItemAmount(995, 70000000)==true) {
	      deleteItem(995, getItemSlot(995), 70000000);
	      sendMessage("YOUR WISH HAS CAME TRUE!");
	      addItem(Item2.randomwell(), 1);
	      sendMessage("Unfortanatly you need to wait 1 HOUR to make another wish!");
	      actionTimer = 3600;[/code]
Then replace all that with
[code]            } else if (useItemID == 962 && atObjectID == 884)// well
              if(actionTimer == 0)
              if(playerHasItemAmount(962, 1)==false) {
	      sendMessage("You Need a christmas cracker to drop in the well");
	      }
	      else if(playerHasItemAmount(962, 1)==true) {
	      deleteItem(995, getItemSlot(962), 1);
	      sendMessage("YOUR WISH HAS CAME TRUE!");
	      addItem(1040, 1);
	      sendMessage("U got a yellow phat from a christmas cracker");
	      actionTimer = 3600;[/code]

